      "text": "Surely men of low degree [are] vanity, [and] men of high degree [are] a lie: to be laid in the balance, they [are] altogether [lighter] than vanity.",
      "versionTitle": "King James Version"
    },
    {
      "language": "en",
      "ref": "Psalm 62:9",
      "source_id": "asv",
      "source_url": "https://ebible.org/eng-asv/PSA062.htm",
      "text": "Surely men of low degree are vanity, and men of high degree are a lie: In the balances they will go up; They are together lighter than vanity.",
      "versionTitle": "American Standard Version"
    },
    {
      "language": "en",
      "ref": "Psalm 62:9",
      "source_id": "web",
      "source_url": "https://ebible.org/engwebp/PSA062.htm",
